Description: VERA BRADLEY'S LARGE DUFFLE - NORTHERN STRIPES PATTERN - A stylish pattern with a combination of pink, red, grey and black & white. Dimensions 22" w x 11 ½" h x 11 ½" d with 15" strap drop A worth while investment for college students and professional ladies who travel now & then. Going home for the weekend or out on a girls' getaway? This duffel will help you pack it all in style. Interior pockets keep your cosmetics, and other "girly gear" in place. The exterior pockets keep boarding passes, reading material or snacks close by. Exterior features a slip pocket on the end and a zip pocket on the front. Inside features three mesh pockets. Zip closure. Machine Washable - Cold Water, Gentle Cycle and Line Dry.
